@startuml SC-16-Dashboard-Global
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Consulter Dashboard Global (SuperAdmin)

object SuperAdmin
object "Interface Dashboard" as DashboardUI
object "Service Analytique" as ServiceAnalytics
object "Service Monitoring" as ServiceMonitoring
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Service Cache" as ServiceCache
object "Service Audit" as ServiceAudit

SuperAdmin --> DashboardUI : 1: acceder("Dashboard Global")
DashboardUI --> ServiceCache : 2: obtenirDonneesDashboard(en_cache)
ServiceCache --> ServiceCache : 3: verifierExpiration()

ServiceCache --> ServiceAnalytics : 4: obtenirMetriques()
ServiceAnalytics --> BaseDonnees : 5: executerRequete(statistiques)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceAnalytics : 5.1: donneesStatistiques
ServiceAnalytics --> ServiceMonitoring : 6: obtenirSanteSysteme()
ServiceMonitoring --> BaseDonnees : 7: executerRequete(monitoring)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceMonitoring : 7.1: donneesSante
ServiceMonitoring --> ServiceAnalytics : 8: statutSante
ServiceAnalytics --> DashboardUI : 9: metriquesDashboard
DashboardUI --> ServiceCache : 10: mettreEnCache(metriques)
ServiceCache --> DashboardUI : 11: mis_en_cache
DashboardUI --> SuperAdmin : 12: afficher(tableau_de_bord)

SuperAdmin --> DashboardUI : 13: filtrer(periode)
DashboardUI --> ServiceAnalytics : 14: obtenirMetriques({dateDebut, dateFin})
ServiceAnalytics --> BaseDonnees : 15: executerRequete(donnees_filtrees)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceAnalytics : 15.1: donneesFiltrees
ServiceAnalytics --> DashboardUI : 16: metriques_filtrees
DashboardUI --> SuperAdmin : 17: montrer(resultats)

SuperAdmin --> DashboardUI : 18: exporter(rapport)
DashboardUI --> ServiceAnalytics : 19: genererRapport()
ServiceAnalytics --> ServiceAnalytics : 20: formaterDonnees()
ServiceAnalytics --> DashboardUI : 21: rapport_PDF

DashboardUI --> ServiceAudit : 21.1: enregistrerAction("EXPORT_RAPPORT_GLOBAL")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 21.2: sauvegarderLog()

DashboardUI --> SuperAdmin : 22: telecharger(rapport_global.pdf)

note right of ServiceAnalytics
Metriques affichees:
- Nombre utilisateurs actifs
- Revenus totaux
- Nombre secretariats
- Statut systeme
- Alertes critiques
end note

@enduml
